Getting Started

Ribosome is a flat-file collection of macros that are run with SAS. Ribosome works best with SAS version >=9.4.

If you don’t have SAS installed on your system, you can download a free copy SAS University Edition for non-commercial use.

If you’re already set up with SAS and are looking for a reference, please have a look at our examples.
